&lt;p>&#xD;
    Tasks, Steps, and associated guidelines provide general guidance to the practitioner. To go one step further, Tool&#xD;
    Mentors are an additional means of providing guidance by showing how to achieve certain goals with a specific software&#xD;
    tool. Tool mentors link Tasks with tools such as Rational Rose, Rational RequisitePro, Rational ClearCase, Rational&#xD;
    ClearQuest, Rational Suite TestStudio. Tool Mentors almost completely encapsulate the dependencies of the content on&#xD;
    the tool set, keeping the tasks free from tool details. An organization can extend the concept of Tool Mentor to&#xD;
    provide guidance for other tools.&#xD;
&lt;/p></mainDescription>
